            "name": "NPC Core pg. 141",
            "type": "link"
          },
          "name": "NPC Core",
          "page": 141,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "The greatest knowledge comes from experience. Village elders, ancient seers, and advisors to royalty are examples of those valued for such wisdom. Sages educate and guide their people from straying from their cultures' norms and traditions.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
