          },
          "effect": "The sage gives the ally a savvy piece of advice, providing valuable insight. The ally gains a +2 circumstance bonus to the triggering roll.",
          "name": "Timely Advice",
          "subtype": "ability",
          "traits": [
            {
              "alternate_link": {
